      "content": "i know i should talk to my doc but they are super hard to reach and i'm honestly exhausted. i've read online that melatonin is just a natural hormone so it shouldn't be a big deal to mix with something like ambien since they just work on different parts of the sleep cycle. it's not like mixing alcohol and pills or anything, right? it seems like it would just make the ambien more effective so i can finally sleep through the night.",
